title: Embassy of Norway in Canberra
text: Norway has an <a href="embassy">embassy</a> in <a href="Canberra">Canberra</a>. The embassy was established in 1947. The embassy has <a href="dual%20accreditation">dual accreditation</a>s to all the other nations of <a href="Oceania">Oceania</a>. Norway also has ten <a href="honorary%20consulate">honorary consulate</a>s in Oceania, five of which are in <a href="Australia">Australia</a> alone.
